item.title: CVE-2019-1010247|2024-08-05T03:07:18.449Z -- zmartzone%20iam -- mod_auth_openidc
item.description: ZmartZone IAM mod_auth_openidc 2.3.10.1 and earlier is affected by: Cross Site Scripting (XSS). The impact is: Redirecting the user to a phishing page or interacting with the application on behalf of the user. The component is: File: src/mod_auth_openidc.c, Line: 3109. The fixed version is: 2.3.10.2.
